ncover new powers to aid you in your quest.<br></li><li>Hidden secrets to discover.<br></li><li>Calming and relaxing to play.<br></li><li>1:1 movement controls allow you to specify your character's path.<br></li><li>Choose your control method, mouse, keyboard or controller.<br></li><li>Family friendly.<br></li><li>Meet friendly characters along the way to help you progress.<br></li><li>A relaxing and calming soundtrack.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687300/extras/3a18cf4759c24e68085ded4b097e09f2.avif?t=1738073724\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
